title: Tracy Morgan, bouncing back from bad crash, returns to 'SNL'
text: > Entertainment Tracy Morgan, bouncing back from bad crash, returns to 'SNL' In this Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015, photo, provided by NBC, comedians Jack McBrayer, from left to right, Tina Fey, Tracy Morgan, Jane Krakowski, and Alec Baldwin stand on stage during a monologue on the show, in New York. Morgan returned to a familiar stage, hosting "Saturday Night Live" in his first appearance on the show since a vehicle crash that left him in a coma. (Dana Edelson/NBC via AP)
